October 11, 2005
                                            
Google, Inc.
Attn: User Support, DMCA Complaints
1600 Amphitheatre Parkway
Mountain View, CA 94043
Fax (650) 618-8507

User Support:

This is our formal complaint against the website owner of www.spiderproxy.com whose site is currently listed in your search engine index. This site is infringing on our copyrighted website information. We request that you review this site and remove the pages listed below from the Google search results until this site owner removes ALL of our website content that has been illegally referenced or copied.


(1) Our Copyrighted material is located here:

http://www.databasesystemscorp.com
http://www.911broadcast.com
http://www.easyivr.com

(2) The offending website pages that contain our copyrighted material is identified below and is maintained on the following URL:

http://www.spiderproxy.com

BACKGROUND

The following documents the copyright infringement by the owner of the above site.

My initial check indicated cached copies of each of our 3 websites
